caption.center: GRIEVANCE ADMINISTRATOR, ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION, STATE
OF MICHIGAN, Petitioner-Appellee, v. DAVID A. WOELKERS,

opinion.opinion_text: On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal from the January 5, 1999 order of the Attorney Discipline Board is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
